{
  "text": "5. Measures that deplete islets of passenger cells (prolonged culture and 95 % 02 atmosphere) do not prevent cytokine mediated betacell damage [CITATION_1] , and passenger-cell depletion has no effect on the ability of either human or rodent islets to produce NO, as detected by nitrite formation (Corbett et al., unpublished data).",
